\pard{\pntext\f2\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf2\pnindent360{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\i     List and discuss five areas of the EULA that stood out to you while reading.\par
{\pntext\f2\'B7\tab}    Did the EULA create any conflicts with how you currently use the software? If so, in what ways? How would you propose to resolve the conflict?\par
